Package: zaro
Title: Zarr via Arrow
Version: 0.0.1.9002
Authors@R: person("Michael", "Sumner", email = "mdsumner@gmail.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Low-level Zarr interface (V2 and V3) built on Arrow filesystem and
    codec infrastructure. Provides direct access to Zarr stores on local
    filesystems, S3, and GCS via Arrow, with fallback to GDAL virtual
    filesystems for HTTP and other protocols via gdalraster. Supports Kerchunk
    JSON and Parquet reference stores for virtual Zarr access to existing
    archives. Automatically detects Zarr version and handles S3 region
    redirects.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
